nodes.text: Incki Kunzler was a Human female Jedi who stayed on Rishi during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire.

Incki Kunzler appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Shadow of Revan, a 2014 Digital Expansion to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, as the Level 60 Basic Gear vendor on Rishi for the Jedi Consular class. Kunzler and the rest of the class gear vendors at Rishi, along with all other Daily Areas and high-level planets, were replaced by a single standardized vendor in Game Update 4.0 on October 20, 2015.
